  "title": "Sales & Marketing Associate",
  "description": "<p><u><strong>Job Summary</strong></u></p>\n<p>Support the sales and marketing team in promoting financial services, products, or solutions to clients, and contribute to the development and execution of sales and marketing strategies.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><u><strong>Key Responsibilities</strong></u></p>\n<p>1. Sales Support: Assist sales team in researching potential clients and preparing sales materials</p>\n<p>2. Marketing Assistance: Help develop and implement marketing campaigns and create marketing materials</p>\n<p>3. Data Analysis: Analyze sales data and market trends to inform sales and marketing strategies.</p>\n<p>4. Client Communication: Assist in responding to client inquiries and providing exceptional customer service.</p>\n<p>5. Project Coordination: Coordinate projects, such as events to promote financial services and products.</p>",
